{"tid":2398140,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"傑斯再被捕！","createTime":"2021-02-07T04:54:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T08:48:36.000Z","uid":211994,"like":9,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"3421453a2581b32a2a4ce7de90c89085da40048e","tid":2398140,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T04:54:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210207/L3W6KRCY6FHVNGEW4XYCWD25VY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210207%2FL3W6KRCY6FHVNGEW4XYCWD25VY%2F&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=2dbc0e20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210207%2FL3W6KRCY6FHVNGEW4XYCWD25VY%2F&h=ca9e2299\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210207/L3W6KRCY6FHVNGEW4XYCWD25VY/</a><br />\n<br />\nD100網台主持傑斯去年初於網上發起眾籌，卻遭警方指控洗黑錢，傑斯、其妻子及女助理去年底涉嫌「洗黑錢」及「資助分裂國家」被捕。警方今日發新聞稿指，國安處經進一步調查後，今日在港島區拘捕傑斯（52歲），涉嫌「作出具煽動意圖的作為」罪，違反香港法例第200章《刑事罪行條例》第10 條。"},{"pid":"5fea3e782b4a28a8d8341b84a98ef5d59183db30","tid":2398140,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T04:58:28.000Z","msg":"Giggs<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e518e11269dc34731b3ab916a028e984139623","tid":2398140,"uid":70489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T04:58:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3fcf7d8bef9d3d7a885f80839ee2758fc56ec3ad","tid":2398140,"uid":70489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T04:59:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"13c056aaaf5bc99af845621bc6013d6b20d9558c","tid":2398140,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T04:59:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7672bf88b7e9728a018d9043f246637f5cd3192","tid":2398140,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T04:59:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06c373599bc2ddbe6613139027