src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955c8d93e46edecf0917b1b32e6915540b5439ed","tid":2398140,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:06:57.000Z","msg":"希望佢平安<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3603357bf08f49d344c457a115e1988d3b43b4eb","tid":2398140,"uid":192528,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:26:53.000Z","msg":"消息指，有人透過計劃籌了千多萬港元，其中動用約600多萬元投資股票<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e3b763f57f8ea85c768759508127a7fad1ae5b","tid":2398140,"uid":361751,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:28:03.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>捨得走未呀<br />\n<br />\nOn99留港撚</strong></span>"},{"pid":"6305397f123e4af22edf94386a204f44883ba699","tid":2398140,"uid":24924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:28:12.000Z","msg":"又黎"},{"pid":"b15b5832e2730ff04e37dfdbd8831ff1dba37bab","tid":2398140,"uid":389613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e8e3b763f57f8ea85c768759508127a7fad1ae5b","tid":2398140,"uid":361751,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:28:03.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>捨得走未呀<br />\n<br />\nOn99留港撚</strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:29:03.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">不論離開定堅守都係手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span> </span><br />\n<br />\n決意堅守陣地既手足，必須時刻警惕提防，保留有用之軀，日後方能煲底相見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我認為中共已撕破臉皮，唔會再講法理情，只餘硬碰硬一著，而港共武裝與抗爭者實力相距太大，難成氣候，除非把抗爭層面擴大化，將火魔、簡易組裝槍械等等變成家家戶戶都有的必備品，否則難以對抗如同送頭，亦無必要，而且傳播該類資訊卻係十分頭痛既議題，能參與者的數量亦成疑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"> <span class=\"red\">今次 BNO 大量港人走資走人逼中共支爆發難，借東風，引天下圍中，百國聯軍，打柒老共，核平北京！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>所以：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"> <span class=\"red\">離開唔係逃避，係主動攬炒救香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>警號已經響起咗！越著時間過去，離開香港將會日漸困難，大時代中不能存有饒幸之心，成日同自己講冇事既、冇事既個d人，就係走唔切，困咗係東德既人。<span class=\"red\">總之任何人，有得即走，特別高風險人士一定要最早走，其他人遲極唔可以遲過外國撤僑，外國第一個國家撤僑你就要跟住飛。外國唔會一次過撤，會比時間同signal香港人走先。</span>切記你係難民唔係移民。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪好好奇美國點解得把口唔出手制裁？我話你知幾時先制裁、有冇可能封關、應唔應該走、幾時要走。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2093986\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2093986</a><br />\n<br />\n(分析)仲有幾耐入東突(新疆)模式，見到咩警告要流亡？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1980175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1980175</a><br />\n<br />\n香港簡易流亡手冊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/478029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/478029</a><br />\n<br />\n[借古鑑今] 中國因逃亡潮於 1951 年 2 月 15 日鎖關，香港因 BNO 鎖關的憂慮正響歐美之間蔓延！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2390806\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2390806</a>"},{"pid":"cae1454407150f0102bf3400519e14b53510e601","tid":2398140,"uid":361751,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b15b5832e2730ff04e37dfdbd8831ff1dba37bab","tid":2398140,"uid":389613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e8e3b763f57f8ea85c768759508127a7fad1ae5b","tid":2398140,"uid":361751,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"cite